http://www.pastebay.net/1070923

What is this? It's clearly not the same thing as the ShipJ uploads, which a lot of us have come to know, love and depend on as containing most (if not all) of the last week's new books. This is clearly not new books. Why call it the same thing? Is ShipJ going to stop his uploads? Strange man, strange.
Thanks for the great uploads. All your work is appreciated. Do you have the new Crossed Badlands 10-11 or Ferals? Thanks again.

I'm too old for internet squabbling, which gets you absolutely nowhere, truth be told.

I was asking an honest question, because I'm confused.

I know Snake from another website, I believe, and I don't have any problems with his efforts here at TPB. 

I just think it's confusing to do this upload with the same name as ShipJ's. I'm sure there will be plenty of people interested in both, regardless of the name. Just call this upload something different.
